08:13.160 --> 08:14.160
- ♪ Yeah ♪
- Max.

08:14.185 --> 08:15.978
♪ I'm feeling heat in December ♪

08:16.003 --> 08:17.845
- ♪ When you're round me ♪
- Do you mind?

08:17.870 --> 08:20.353
