08:29.462 --> 08:31.650
♪ You're the medicine and the pain ♪

08:31.675 --> 08:33.602
♪ The tattoo inside my brain ♪

08:33.628 --> 08:36.236
♪ And, baby, you know it's obvious ♪

08:36.260 --> 08:38.073
What's obvious?

08:38.097 --> 08:41.409
