- Oh, God, really?

08:41.434 --> 08:45.449
♪ You say the word,
and I'll go anywhere blindly ♪

08:45.474 --> 08:48.970
♪ I'm a sucker for you, yeah ♪

08:48.995 --> 08:52.869
♪ Any road you take,
you know that you'll find me ♪

08:52.894 --> 08:56.407
